=## ✅ YouTube Short Created!

**Band:** {{ $json.bandName }}
**Date:** {{ $json.postDate }}
**Status:** {{ $json.status }}

**Next Steps:**
1. Add video link to `mediaLink` field in Obsidian
2. Edit caption if needed
3. When ready, change status to `ready`
4. n8n will then upload to YouTube Shorts

**File:** {{ $json.filename }}
